│ in `llvm/lib/Transforms/Utils/SimplifyCFG.cpp`.\n\n5. Conclusion:\n\nBy adding a check for `PoisonValue` alongside the existing `UndefValue` check, we prevent the invalid cast that causes the assertion      │
